前<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://investors.fiskerinc.com/news/news-details/2023/Fisker-Makes-First-22-Deliveries-of-Fisker-Ocean-SUV-to-Customers-in-the-United-States/default.aspx">才开始</a>发货。 Ocean（在 Fisker 的“碳中和”奥地利格拉茨工厂制造）的基本型号售价为 37,500 美元，续航里程为 350 英里的 550 HP Ocean Extreme 售价高达 69,000 美元。</p><p> Fisker 正在开发一款更实惠的电动汽车，即四门 Pear，不含任何激励措施的起价为 29,900 美元。该车的详细信息也不是很多，但预计将于明年在<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.autoweek.com/news/green-cars/a43272626/what-the-29900-fisker-pear-ev-promises-details/">俄亥俄州洛兹敦</a>开始生产，富士康作为合同制造商。两家公司计划最终每年生产至少 250,000 台。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/fisker-gives-the-best-look-yet-at-its-600-mile-range-ronin-ev-114048266.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/fisker-gives-the-best-look-yet-at-its-600-mile-range-ronin-ev-114048266.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> f9e88d13-62dc-445b-99c9-95ccd5a3857e</guid><dc:creator>史蒂夫·登特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Wed, 05 Jul 2023 11:40:48 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1688556144</ingested><modified> 2023-07-05T11:22:30+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Automotive Industry]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Steve Dent]]></category><media:content height="746" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-07/8f15b4b0-1b1d-11ee-bdf9-909f80037c65" width="1080"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="746" medium="image" url="https: